      • createPattern

        public abstract Pattern createPattern(boolean testRelease,
                                      ContentSubType contentSubType,
                                      ReleaseIdentifier currentReleaseIdentifier,
                                      String relativeRoot)
        Creates a regular expression pattern for this release file.
        Parameters:
        testRelease - true if the release is considered a test release, false otherwise
        contentSubType - the subtype to look for (snapshot, delta or full content)
        currentReleaseIdentifier - the release identifier to use when creating the pattern (wildcard or already matched, exact)
        relativeRoot - the relative directory root to use (wildcard or already matched, exact)
        Returns:
        a compiled pattern for matching against a list of file names
